    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Transfer the mixture to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong></p><p>Top with the <strong>cheesy breadcrumbs</strong> followed by your<strong> smoked streaky bacon </strong>and put the dish in the oven for 20-25 min or until it is golden and bubbling and the bacon is crisp – this is your <strong>bacon & pesto mac 'n' cheese</strong></p><p>Tip: Put the dish on the top shelf of the oven to help crisp up the bacon!</p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
